{"tid":934281,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連登仔知己 女德班教小孩：換男友會爛手爛腳　","createTime":"2018-12-09T07:04:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-09T07:21:11.000Z","uid":72009,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"dd7490146f23cebc26c986500c05d436a33daa60","tid":934281,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T07:04:41.000Z","msg":"媒體揭露一段今年8月臥底遼寧省撫順市夏令營所拍攝的影片，從偷拍上課的畫面中可見，現場人員向學員播放一段女德班演講影片，裡面竟稱女孩若頻換男友，手腳就會長出壞疽，最後壞死截肢。影片中還有名女子自稱以前很愛打扮時髦、穿著裸露，但她接著說：「這不就等同於教別人來侮辱我、強姦我一樣嗎？」<br />\n據報導，該夏令營的參加學員均為5至18歲兒童少年和其家長。有女童向臥底記者表示，以前自己對於男女不平等待遇會感到生氣，但現在聽了老師解釋「男是天、女是地」後就懂了，老師還跟她們說，若一個家庭是女主外、男主內，「他們家以後肯定會敗」。<br />\n畫面曝光後，當地網友紛紛痛批這種夏令營根本是邪教：「這都2018年了，這是邪教啊，沒人取締嗎？」、「關鍵是還有人信&hellip;」、「什麼樣的父母才會送孩子去這樣的地方，簡直是邪教啊」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20181209/1480542\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20181209%2F1480542&d=PSRvB71USbKvCiCuTlXTSf1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=6e110cf8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20181209%2F1480542&h=21e6d92d\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20181209/1480542</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181209/640_2ad6d23e77706b1564bc0678aa317d3c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181209%2F640_2ad6d23e77706b1564bc0678aa317d3c.jpg&h=b865fe1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b15cac793e6ca84a0805701e025a7c21632ac4c","tid":934281,"uid":49918,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T07:07:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c2b33161fc506e7e2e6a7fce3d2b2f9987f1b20b","tid":934281,"uid":126866,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T07:07:35.000Z","msg":"港女應該要去下"},{"pid":"069318b5a317ea432b1fbddaf48283a3bc03e45f","tid":934281,"uid":121355,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"2b15cac793e6ca84a0805701e025a7c21632ac4c","tid":934281,"uid":49918,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T07:07:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T07:11:33.000Z","msg":"連登"},{"pid":"21404ff86ef2cae084600178e9a5f4c84d4c4009","tid":934281,"uid":15830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T07:14:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"093b2ad8e0b8ecc276bd2929a07af49cae43ee7a","tid":934281,"uid":163291,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T07:21:11.000Z","msg":"若一個家庭是女主外、男主內，「他們家以後肯定會敗」。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我知想講女人唔應該出去做野露面，但踩埋男人顧唔到家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}